4. **Wait for Migrations to Run**: The command will run the database migrations specified in your `ormconfig.json` file. This may take some time depending on the complexity of your migrations.
5. **Check Database Status**: After the migrations are complete, verify the status of your database to ensure that the new tables and data have been created as expected.